    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-1" >
      <div class="text-center mt-3 mb-5">
        <span class="h3 border-bottom border-dark mt-3 mb-2"><strong>人気コミック<strong class="rank">Top5</strong></strong></span>
